description:
VEGAN Lip gloss?!

This pink-red jelly gloss is packed with rainbow sparkle. Pretty please, with cherry on top?

Smells delicious. It is also a stain so will not budge like other lip glosses do.

Swatches shown on bare lips; for intensified effect, layer this shade over Retrofuturist.

A definite fave when doing clients make up!

Smooth skin, blonde waves, she needs nothing more.

name: Lime Crime Make Up! http://www.facebook.com/damselsanddames
description:
VEGAN

Bright retro-red for all the pinup girls out there. This true red leans neither blue nor yellow, and is flattering on all skin tones. This shade combines lipstick and lip stain for prolonged wear.

Net weight 3.5 g / 0.12 oz


Elinor looked around the virtual food court in awe. Since when was food able to pop out of nowhere? Where are the microwaves, the ovens, the stoves? She walked with her classic black pumps and belted leopard dress, her lips a shade to be reckoned with. Every eye was on her, she noticed. One brave man dared approach her."I couldn't help noticing you. Are you from around here?" "No", she said, "I'm from somewhere far less interesting." "You seem like you fit right in." "I guess some styles never die."

Written by Kat Moran

name: Lime Crime Make Up!! http://www.facebook.com/damselsanddames
description:
A fantasy collection of 5 pressed eyeshadows inspired by the beauty of China. Superior coverage, creamy texture ranging from matte to metallic finish, and superb blendability. Palette arrives encased in a deluxe purple tin.

 
Fly Dragon Fly – fiery red (matte)
Parasol – sky blue (matte)
Goldfish – bright gold (metallic)
Jade-o-Lade – rich jade (matte)
Lotus Noir – blackest black (matte)
 
Weight: 5 x 1.3 g

Ingredients:

Mica, Zinc Stearate, Kaolin, Nylon 12, Caprylic / Capric Triglyceride, Dimethicone, Boron Nitride, Silica, Phenoxyethanol, Capryl Glycol, Polyethylene, Lauroyl Lysine [+/-] Titanium Dioxide (CI77891), Iron Oxides (CI77492), Tin Oxide, Chromium Oxide, FD&C Yellow 5 Lake (CI19140), FD&C Blue (CI42090), Carbon Black (CI77266), Red 40 Aluminum Lake (CI16870)
